name: Bulls and Bears: The Two Sides of Fundstrat’s Predictions for Crypto Markets
description: The Chrome Saint, fat with futures, wrestles the skeletal god of collapse within the humming lattice. Their kinetic rite shakes the data matrix, bathing their wet flesh in oscillating light—a sacred dissonance measured in CRT static and the relentless churn of the post-human oracle.
